6. Core Business Rules

BR-INV-001

Every inventory item requires barcode.

BR-INV-002

Barcode must be unique.

BR-INV-003

Sold inventory cannot be edited.

BR-INV-004

Stock movement history immutable.

BR-INV-005

Negative stock not allowed.

BR-INV-006

Inventory valuation updated automatically.

BR-INV-007

Barcode printing supported.

BR-INV-008

Inventory linked to purchase record.

