10. Inventory Valuation Engine

Purpose

Calculate stock value.

⸻

Cost Valuation Formula

Inventory\ Value = Quantity \times Cost\ Price

⸻

Retail Valuation Formula

Retail\ Value = Quantity \times Selling\ Price

⸻

Margin Formula

Margin\ Percentage = \frac{Selling\ Price - Cost\ Price}{Cost\ Price} \times 100

